            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "(Huh? That's Monika... And Leon? What are they talking about...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "In other words, Sophie's personality has been like that for a long time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "That's right. She was about the same back when she was a child, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "That's actually really easy to imagine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Sophie hasn't changed much since long ago."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "...I see, I got it. Sorry for taking so much of your time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Oh no, it was enjoyable for me too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, I'll be going now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Ah, okay. I'll see you again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "(...They were talking about me, weren't they?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "(Wait, are they talking behind my back!? Uu, did I do something bad...?)"
        }
    ]
